Package <Unnamed>

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    drsa.DRSA
    Deterministic RSA module that produces the parameters of a RSA key pair from a N bytes pseudo-random seed.
    drsa.PRBG
    Pseudo-random Byte Generator (PRGB) that uses PBKDF2 and a XorShift implementation to produce pseudo-random bytes from a given password, confusion string and iteration counter.
    drsa.randgen
    This application implements the Pseudo-random Byte Generator (drsa.PRBG).
    It may do one of two things:
    - Perform benchmarking of the drsa.PRBG setup - uses random passwords and multiple confusion strings and iteration counters to test the setup of the generator, and produces a histogram with the processing time per confusion string size [1-4], for each iteration count {1, 5, 10, 20, 50, 100, 200}.
    drsa.rsagen
    This application implements the drsa.DRSA module (drsa.DRSA).
